&lt;p data-sourcepos=&quot;17:1-17:19&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-sourcepos=&quot;19:1-27:0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;19:1-19:128&quot;&gt;Become a product expert on the 10Beauty machine, our innovative nail pods, and the accompanying app&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;19:1-19:128&quot;&gt;Manicure touch ups and fixes may be required&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;20:1-20:132&quot;&gt;Proactively approach and engage customers, sharing the story of 10Beauty and the benefits of our products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;21:1-21:143&quot;&gt;Provide compelling, hands-on demonstrations of the 10Beauty machine, showcasing its ease of use and unique features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;22:1-22:205&quot;&gt;Answer customer questions, provide basic troubleshooting for the machine or app, and offer &quot;nail touch-ups&quot; or quick demonstrations to highlight the quality and convenience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;23:1-23:112&quot;&gt;Encourage customers to try the machine!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;24:1-24:128&quot;&gt;Maintain a professional, enthusiastic, and positive image that aligns with the 10Beauty brand values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;25:1-25:125&quot;&gt;Listen to customer feedback and share insights with the 10Beauty team to help us continuously improve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;26:1-27:0&quot;&gt;Ensure the machine and surrounding area are clean, organized, and inviting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;30:1-30:119&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience&lt;/strong&gt; in cosmetology or most preferably nail related work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;30:1-30:119&quot;&gt;Experience working with nails. Will consider a licensed nail tech, a licensed cosmetologist or a nail tech in training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;35:1-35:111&quot;&gt;Punctual, dependable, and always ready to represent 10Beauty positively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-sourcepos=&quot;36:1-36:92&quot;&gt;Ability to work retail hours, including weekends and holidays, as needed&lt;/li&gt;
